    "body": "@Legend-Master The existing `additional_plugins_path` and the new `signed_plugins_path` resolve to **different directories**.\r\n\r\nWhen signing is enabled, the bundler copies plugins into two separate locations:\r\n\r\n| Variable | Resolved path | Contents |\r\n|---|---|---|\r\n| `additional_plugins_path` (existing) | `<output>/Plugins/x86-unicode/additional/` | `nsis_tauri_utils.dll` only |\r\n| `signed_plugins_path` (new) | `<output>/Plugins/x86-unicode/` | stock plugins (`NSISdl` / `StartMenu` / `System` / `nsDialogs`) |\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri/blob/41fdca7d1991cf4b4b69a5a758a5371333218487/crates/tauri-bundler/src/bundle/windows/nsis/mod.rs#L201\r\nhttps://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri/blob/41fdca7d1991cf4b4b69a5a758a5371333218487/crates/tauri-bundler/src/bundle/windows/nsis/mod.rs#L244-L260\r\n\r\nThe stock plugins live **one level above** where `additional_plugins_path` points, so the existing `!addplugindir` doesn't cover them.",
