    "body": "I think I had a git stash conflict that I didn't notice that pushed the `!addplugindir` in this PR a bit lower which gave me\r\n\r\n```\r\nPlugin command System::Call conflicts with a plugin in another directory!\r\nError in macro __NSD_FreeImage on macroline 2\r\nError in macro MUI_FUNCTION_WELCOMEPAGE on macroline 50\r\nError in macro MUI_PAGEDECLARATION_WELCOME on macroline 18\r\nError in macro MUI_PAGE_WELCOME on macroline 6\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt's working now after resetting the workspace, sorry about that! Appreciate the effort digging this!",
